OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FNew footage has been released showing
OL,7,Fthe murderer of student Henry Nowak
OL,8,Frepeatedly lying to police, falsely
OL,9,Fclaiming he'd been racially attacked,
OL,10,Fas ITV News' Amy Lewis reports
OL,12,FFurther police body-worn video footage
OL,13,Fhas been released showing Vickrum
OL,14,FDigwa lying to officers that he had
OL,15,Fbeen "racially attacked" by student
OL,16,FHenry Nowak.
OL,26,@wD@FOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
