OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782501495
OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FDigwa, 23, was jailed for life with a
OL,7,Fminimum term of 21 years on June 1 for
OL,8,Fthe murder of Mr Nowak, 18, in
OL,9,FSouthampton, after falsely claiming Mr
OL,10,FNowak had racially abused him.
OL,12,FAnger erupted after a three-minute
OL,13,Fpolice body-worn video was released
OL,14,Fshowing Mr Nowak, from Chafford
OL,15,FHundred, Essex, being placed in
OL,16,Fhandcuffs moments before he became
OL,17,Funconscious and subsequently died.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
