OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782501495
OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FNew footage has been released during
OL,7,Fwhich Digwa tells officers at the
OL,8,Fscene what were described in court as
OL,9,F"wicked lies" about Mr Nowak,
OL,10,Fincluding saying he was drunk and had
OL,11,Fracially attacked him.
OL,13,FHe also denies any knowledge when
OL,14,Fasked about a wound suffered by Mr
OL,15,FNowak.
OL,17,FSeparately, Hampshire Constabulary has
OL,18,Fconfirmed that after being arrested,
OL,19,FDigwa was not handcuffed apart from
OL,20,Fwhen he was being transported to and
OL,21,Ffrom court.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
