OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn the footage, Digwa tells the
OL,12,Fofficer: "I was literally just walking
OL,13,Fin and I've seen her. He's then barged
OL,14,Finto me. I kinda said to him,
OL,15,F'Clearly, you're drunk'. I could
OL,16,Fsmell, like you can smell the alcohol."
OL,26,@tD@JOUxD@gO]
