OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FHe continues to say that Mr Nowak
OL,7,Fcalled him a racial slur before saying
OL,8,Fto Digwa that he was a "bad man" and
OL,9,FDigwa responding "Yeah, I'm a bad man"
OL,10,Fas Mr Nowak started recording him.
OL,12,FHe continues: "Obviously, then I just
OL,13,Fpush him away, he's then grabbed me,
OL,14,Fthen started grabbing my turban and
OL,15,Fpulled my hair, started grabbing my
OL,16,Fhair, he was, like, punching me and
OL,17,Fall that sort of stuff."
OL,26,@pD@XOUpD@`O]qD@ROUqD@fO]tD@OOUyD@XO]
