OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FAfter Digwa is arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder, he tells the
OL,8,Fofficer: "I have been racially
OL,9,Fattacked."
OL,11,FThe court heard that Digwa had lied
OL,12,Fabout the allegation of being racially
OL,13,Fattacked and the trial was also told
OL,14,Fthat Mr Nowak's alcohol intake was
OL,15,Fbelow the drink-drive limit.
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@JO]
