OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782501495
OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FA longer transcript of separate
OL,7,Ffootage previously released by the
OL,8,FCrown Prosecution Service, first
OL,9,Fobtained by the BBC, showed the moment
OL,10,Fofficers realised Mr Nowak had been
OL,11,Fstabbed.
OL,13,FIn body-worn camera footage from the
OL,14,Fincident, Mr Nowak can be heard
OL,15,Frepeatedly saying: "I've been
OL,16,Fstabbed," to which an officer replies:
OL,17,F"You've been stabbed? Whereabouts?
OL,18,FDon't think you have, mate."
OL,26,@wD@TOUxD@IO]yD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
