PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782501495
OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FThe officer later says "he's saying
OL,7,Fhe's been stabbed so let's just check
OL,8,Fhim and see", and a female police
OL,9,Fofficer calls for an ambulance,
OL,10,Fdescribing how Mr Nowak's pupils are
OL,11,Fnot reacting before the video ends.
OL,13,FIn the transcript, at three minutes
OL,14,Fand five seconds, an officer
OL,15,Fidentified as police officer one said:
OL,16,F"I'm not sure he's breathing."
OL,18,FThey proceed to uncuff Mr Nowak and
OL,19,Fstart CPR.
OL,26,@nD@XOUpD@LO]xD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
