PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782501495
OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FAfter seven minutes and 33 seconds,
OL,7,Fthe officer cuts his clothing and
OL,8,Fpolice officer one asks if he has been
OL,9,Fstabbed there, with an unseen gesture.
OL,11,FThe female officer replies: "Yes, he's
OL,12,Fgot a stab... there's a mark there."
OL,14,FPolice officer one continues chest
OL,15,Fcompressions and then a paramedic
OL,16,Farrives on the scene.
OL,18,FPolice officer one tells him "we just
OL,19,Fdiscovered a stab wound in his chest".
OL,26,@sD@]OUtD@dO]zD@^OU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
