OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782501495
OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FThe recording ends after eight minutes
OL,7,Fand 49 seconds.
OL,9,FIt was released with no objection from
OL,10,FMr Nowak's family, and after
OL,11,Fconsultation with Hampshire
OL,12,FConstabulary.
OL,14,FAfter the case, temporary Deputy Chief
OL,15,FConstable Robert France of Hampshire
OL,16,FConstabulary apologised on behalf of
OL,17,Fthe officers, but said they were "lied
OL,18,Fto" and would have been unaware of Mr
OL,19,FNowak's injury which he said would not
OL,20,Fhave been obvious.
OL,26,@yD@bOUzD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782501495
OL,3,CNewly released video shows Henry Nowak
OL,4,Ckiller 'lying' to police officers
OL,6,FHe said: "I want to apologise, I want
OL,7,Fto say that I am sorry that Henry
OL,8,Fcouldn't be saved that night. I'm
OL,9,Fsorry that he was handcuffed and
OL,10,Farrested in the moments before he lost
OL,11,Fconsciousness."
OL,13,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,14,FConduct is investigating Hampshire
OL,15,FPolice's response in Mr Nowak's case.
OL,17,FThe jury inquest into his death next
OL,18,Fyear at Winchester Coroner's Court
OL,19,Fwill also look at whether any "act or
OL,20,Fomission by a police officer" caused
OL,21,For contributed to his death.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@OO]{D@_OU|D@]O]
